name: Whitehorse Gold Corp.
shortDescription: Whitehorse Gold is focused on its wholly owned Skukum Gold Project located in the Whitehorse Mining District of the southern Yukon.
longDescription: Whitehorse Gold is focused on its wholly owned Skukum Gold Project located in the Whitehorse Mining District of the southern Yukon. The project consists of 1,051 mineral claims covering an area of 170 square kilometres and is located approximately 55 kilometres south of Whitehorse, Yukon. The project hosts the advanced-stage Skukum Creek, Goddell and Mount Skukum high-grade gold deposits and multiple high-priority exploration targets. Project infrastructure includes an all-weather access road, an all-weather 50-person camp, approximately 4.8 kilometres of underground workings, an extensive surface road network and a previously operating 300-tpd mill along with a tailings management facility and service buildings.
fullAddress: 1066 West Hastings Street, Suite 1750, Toronto, ON, CA

longDescription: Wildpack Beverage Inc is engaged in the Beverage Packaging and Production Industry. The Company has three reportable segments, being can filling, can decorating, and corporate. longDescription: Wishpond Technologies Ltd is a provider of marketing-focused online business solutions providing digital marketing solutions that empower entrepreneurs to achieve success online. It replaces entire marketing functions in an easy-to-use product, for a fraction of the cost. The company employs a Software-as-a-Service (SaaS) business model where substantially all its revenue is subscription-based recurring revenue.
